Published: 13 March 2026

Effect of climate-driven childhood sleep erosion on potential regional economic inequality
                    Bowen Chu 
            ORCID: orcid.org/0000-0002-3484-40551, Xiang Liu 
            ORCID: orcid.org/0000-0002-2748-95502, Yijing Zhu1,3, Jianfeng Luo1, Lan Luo 
            ORCID: orcid.org/0009-0007-5336-64004, Jiuyi Chen1, Duzitian Li5, Haotian Zheng6, Yi Peng 
